<CD-RAT><Entry><HWD>VOCAB</HWD><Activity><GapFillDropdown layer="1" h="420" w="670" y="10" x="10"><Title alignment="left" isOn="1">Work, lifestyle and health<br /></Title><Instruction alignment="left" isOn="1"><FONT FACE="Verdana">Click </FONT>on the correct words or phrases.<br /></Instruction><ReferenceObject soundIsOn="0" videoIsOn="0" defaultHeight="196" alignment="left" isOn="1"><Asset file="06093101.jpg" folder="images/" h="186" w="247" y="-1" x="211" layer="1" type="graphic" /></ReferenceObject><ScrollableAssets /><Content><FONT FACE="Verdana">It is predicted that our </FONT><Dropdown default-text="Choose"><Score num="1" /><Choice><FONT FACE="Verdana">lifeway</FONT></Choice><Choice><FONT FACE="Verdana">life habit</FONT></Choice><Choice is-correct="1"><FONT FACE="Verdana">lifestyle</FONT></Choice></Dropdown><FONT FACE="Verdana"> in fifty years&apos; time will be very different to what we enjoy today. For example computer </FONT><Dropdown default-text="Choose"><Score num="1" /><Choice><FONT FACE="Verdana">meetings</FONT></Choice><Choice is-correct="1"><FONT FACE="Verdana">conferencing</FONT></Choice><Choice><FONT FACE="Verdana">get-togethers</FONT></Choice></Dropdown><FONT FACE="Verdana"> will save time and money as we see our overseas colleagues on the computer rather than in person, but the social </FONT><Dropdown default-text="Choose"><Score num="1" /><Choice><FONT FACE="Verdana">action</FONT></Choice><Choice><FONT FACE="Verdana">inaction</FONT></Choice><Choice is-correct="1"><FONT FACE="Verdana">interaction</FONT></Choice></Dropdown><FONT FACE="Verdana"> involved in seeing our colleagues in person will be lost. Likewise, an increase in </FONT><Dropdown default-text="Choose"><Score num="1" /><Choice><FONT FACE="Verdana">offline</FONT></Choice><Choice is-correct="1"><FONT FACE="Verdana">online</FONT></Choice><Choice><FONT FACE="Verdana">computer</FONT></Choice></Dropdown><FONT FACE="Verdana"> shopping means that once thriving city centres could become </FONT><Dropdown default-text="Choose"><Score num="1" /><Choice is-correct="1"><FONT FACE="Verdana">wastelands</FONT></Choice><Choice><FONT FACE="Verdana">waste places</FONT></Choice><Choice><FONT FACE="Verdana">waste spots</FONT></Choice></Dropdown><FONT FACE="Verdana"> with not a shopper in sight.</FONT><br /><FONT FACE="Verdana">Of course this </FONT><Dropdown default-text="Choose"><Score num="1" /><Choice><FONT FACE="Verdana">sitting</FONT></Choice><Choice><FONT FACE="Verdana">reclining</FONT></Choice><Choice is-correct="1"><FONT FACE="Verdana">sedentary</FONT></Choice></Dropdown><FONT FACE="Verdana"> way of life does not auger well for our health. </FONT><Dropdown default-text="Choose"><Score num="1" /><Choice><FONT FACE="Verdana">Fatness</FONT></Choice><Choice><FONT FACE="Verdana">Overweight</FONT></Choice><Choice is-correct="1"><FONT FACE="Verdana">Obesity</FONT></Choice></Dropdown><FONT FACE="Verdana">, for example, could become more commonplace as a result of </FONT><Dropdown default-text="Choose"><Score num="1" /><Choice><FONT FACE="Verdana">unactivity</FONT></Choice><Choice><FONT FACE="Verdana">activity</FONT></Choice><Choice is-correct="1"><FONT FACE="Verdana">inactivity</FONT></Choice></Dropdown><FONT FACE="Verdana">. Looking on the bright side, the </FONT><Dropdown default-text="Choose"><Score num="1" /><Choice><FONT FACE="Verdana">pleasure</FONT></Choice><Choice is-correct="1"><FONT FACE="Verdana">leisure</FONT></Choice><Choice><FONT FACE="Verdana">displeasure</FONT></Choice></Dropdown><FONT FACE="Verdana"> and fitness industry should be thriving with people eager to keep fit and escape the social </FONT><Dropdown default-text="Choose"><Score num="1" /><Choice><FONT FACE="Verdana">isolating</FONT></Choice><Choice><FONT FACE="Verdana">isolated</FONT></Choice><Choice is-correct="1"><FONT FACE="Verdana">isolation</FONT></Choice></Dropdown><FONT FACE="Verdana"> of conducting much of their activities from their computer screen!</FONT></Content></GapFillDropdown><